3) Office Products - Telephone cords are commonly used in office settings, so this category is also likely.
4) Office & School Supplies - Similar to the previous category, the product can be used in both office and school environments.
5) Industrial & Scientific - While less likely, the product could also be used in industrial or scientific settings that require telephone connectivity.

Note: The other categories listed are less likely because they are not directly related to telephone accessories or office supplies.
